item.title: How many Python versions are in your Windows 10? I had five.
item.description: 2020-03-10 Update1: How many types of Python does your macOS contain? I had 401 kinds. Update2: Karikan Cancer Insurance 2020-03-15 Update3: The title was Window 10 and it was fixed to Windows 10. It was an unconscious typo. The title is fanatic. On WSL Ubuntu 18.04, there were 3 types via pyenv + 2 types from OS, for a total of 10 types. Why I tried to write this article I will explain the background.
